Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Construct A', 3: 'Hey, take a look at that...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Construct A', 3: "Is that a frame for real? It's so beautiful...", 4: '1'}
{2: "They're all looking this way.", 3: '10', 4: "Someone's complimenting you.", 5: '12'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'The Support Force mentioned that the frame would be a little lavish when they delivered it. I thought they were just joking...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'Even though the appearance of the frame is a little too excessive, the gain in benefits is also significant.', 4: '1'}

{2: 'Liv', 3: 'In terms of combat, the new frame allows for tactical positioning through satellite geolocation. Plus, I can move and shoot in the same way Lee does with the new tactical mode.', 4: '1'}
{2: "I also think that you've become much stronger, Liv.", 3: '17', 4: "But don't go dashing to the frontline immediately, Liv.", 5: '18'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "That was... an accident. I was still familiarizing myself with the new frame, you seeâ€”I'll pay more attention next time...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: 'There will be more members joining us in the future, Commandant. I want to be a role model worthy of their respect and someone they can learn from...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "That's why I'm glad to equip this advanced frame.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Do you think it's possible for me to use another frame on non-combat missions in the future, Commandant?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "It's kind of embarrassing how everyone keeps staring at me...", 4: '1'}
